        <dd><em>Encyclop&aelig;dia Britannica Online</em>, s. v. "gun control", accessed February 12, 2015, <span class="citation-url">http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/683775/gun-control</span>.</dd>
    </dl>

    <p class="md-citations-warning">
        While every effort has been made to follow citation style rules, there may be some discrepancies.<br/>
        Please refer to the appropriate style manual or other sources if you have any questions.
    </p>

